Hello everyone,

I'm looking for a solution to a problem of backup and file sync between two
computers. I have the following requirements, and I wonder if what I want
is realistic and is there off the shelf software I can use.

I have several laptops and a desktop that I would like to back up and keep
in sync.
-------------- next part --------------
