From lists at alteeve.ca  Fri Feb 20 02:09:02 2015
From: lists at alteeve.ca (Digimer)
Date: Thu, 19 Feb 2015 21:09:02 -0500
Subject: [GTALUG] Fw: [Cryptography] Lenovo laptops with preloaded
 adware and an evil CA
In-Reply-To: <20150220014116.6037648.33221.16678@gmail.com>
